messages.message: Yuna: You may be a maester, but I will still fight!{N}Seymour: Your eyes, they burn with resolve...{N}Beautiful.
Tidus: I knew you were bad news the first time we met!{N}Seymour: Oh, my sincerest apologies.{N}Tidus: Seymour!
Wakka: Maester! We must stop this!{N}Seymour: ...{N}Wakka: This can't be happening!
Seymour: Yuna...you would pity me now?
Seymour: That power that defeated Anima...{N}It will be mine!
Seymour: Feel my pain! Come, Anima!
